Usage: set_threshold_voltage_group [-help] [-hinst <string>] -name <group_name>
                                   [-override] {-libraries <library list> | -lib_cells <lib cell list>}

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <string>               # Specify the hinst (string, optional)
-lib_cells <lib cell list>    # lib_cells to be defined in the VT group
                              # (string, optional)
-libraries <library list>     # libraries to be defined in the VT group
                              # (string, optional)
-name <group_name>            # Name of the VT group (string, required)
-override                     # override liberty defined VT groups
                              # (bool, optional)